reviewText: Really liked it but a little slow in the beginning!
Big Steven Seagal fan, it did not disappoint
this is a great movie and for anyone who is a Steven Seagal fan I would suggest getting this movie

This Seagal movie is a stinker and deserves less than one star.  I guess I'm still expecting to see him as the exciting martial arts fighter he was 20 years ago, but he doesn't show it anymore in his movies.  This will be my last of his shows that I'll waste anymore money on.

  The seller on the other hand is a winner and is excellent across the board!  I highly recommend this seller to anyone!
